        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (pos &amp;lt; end) {
-               uint64_t mirror_end;
+               uint64_t mirror_end = LUSTRE_EOF;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;and this breaks sanity-flr/42:&lt;/p&gt;
